{
  "entries": [
    {
      "id": "SCN_W_001",
      "category": "window",
      "text": "车窗外，一排倒塌的电线杆向后掠过，铁锈色的横臂像伸出的手指。",
      "weight": 35,
      "duration": 6,
      "edge_types": [],
      "edge_ids": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": []
    },
    {
      "id": "SCN_W_002",
      "category": "window",
      "text": "远处的地平线上，几根烟囱的残影融进灰蓝色的天际。",
      "weight": 35,
      "duration": 5,
      "edge_types": [],
      "edge_ids": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 0.7],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": []
    },
    {
      "id": "SCN_W_003",
      "category": "window",
      "text": "路边长满了叫不出名字的野草，在风里一浪一浪地倒伏。",
      "weight": 35,
      "duration": 5,
      "edge_types": ["path"],
      "edge_ids": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": []
    },
    {
      "id": "SCN_W_004",
      "category": "window",
      "text": "一辆翻倒的公交车半埋在沙土里，车窗上还贴着褪色的广告。",
      "weight": 30,
      "duration": 6,
      "edge_types": ["main_road"],
      "edge_ids": [],
      "progress_range": [0.1, 0.9],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": []
    },
    {
      "id": "SCN_W_005",
      "category": "window",
      "text": "天边堆着厚重的云层，像一座座灰色的山脉。",
      "weight": 30,
      "duration": 5,
      "edge_types": [],
      "edge_ids": [],
      "progress_range": [0.3, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": []
    },
    {
      "id": "SCN_C_001",
      "category": "cabin",
      "text": "仪表盘上的小摆件随着颠簸轻轻晃动，发出细碎的声响。",
      "weight": 25,
      "duration": 5,
      "edge_types": [],
      "edge_ids": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": []
    },
    {
      "id": "SCN_C_002",
      "category": "cabin",
      "text": "方向盘的皮套已经磨得发亮了，上面有两道深深的指痕。",
      "weight": 25,
      "duration": 5,
      "edge_types": [],
      "edge_ids": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 0.5],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": []
    },
    {
      "id": "SCN_C_003",
      "category": "cabin",
      "text": "副驾座位上放着陶夏的笔记本，翻到了画着路线草图的那一页。",
      "weight": 20,
      "duration": 6,
      "edge_types": [],
      "edge_ids": [],
      "progress_range": [0.2, 0.8],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": []
    },
    {
      "id": "SCN_S_001",
      "category": "sound",
      "text": "远处传来几声鸟鸣，在空旷的废墟间回荡了很久。",
      "weight": 15,
      "duration": 5,
      "edge_types": ["path"],
      "edge_ids": [],
      "progress_range": [0.2, 0.8],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": []
    },
    {
      "id": "SCN_S_002",
      "category": "sound",
      "text": "轮胎碾过碎石的声音变得均匀起来，像一首单调的催眠曲。",
      "weight": 15,
      "duration": 5,
      "edge_types": [],
      "edge_ids": [],
      "progress_range": [0.4, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": []
    },
    {
      "id": "SCN_T_001",
      "category": "time",
      "text": "日头偏西了，车影在路面上拉得越来越长。",
      "weight": 15,
      "duration": 5,
      "edge_types": [],
      "edge_ids": [],
      "progress_range": [0.6, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": []
    },
    {
      "id": "SCN_T_002",
      "category": "time",
      "text": "晨雾还没散尽，前方的路像是蒙了一层薄纱。",
      "weight": 15,
      "duration": 5,
      "edge_types": [],
      "edge_ids": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 0.3],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": []
    },
    {
      "id": "SCN_T_003",
      "category": "time",
      "text": "光线在变。云层的缝隙里漏出一道金色，扫过废墟又消失了。",
      "weight": 15,
      "duration": 6,
      "edge_types": [],
      "edge_ids": [],
      "progress_range": [0.3, 0.7],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": []
    },
    {
      "id": "SCN_M_001",
      "category": "micro",
      "text": "路边的废墟墙上，有人用喷漆写了一行字，但已经看不清了。",
      "weight": 10,
      "duration": 6,
      "edge_types": ["main_road"],
      "edge_ids": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": []
    },
    {
      "id": "SCN_M_002",
      "category": "micro",
      "text": "一只瘦弱的野猫蹲在路基上，目送货车驶过，没有躲开。",
      "weight": 10,
      "duration": 6,
      "edge_types": [],
      "edge_ids": [],
      "progress_range": [0.2, 0.9],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": []
    },
    {
      "id": "SCN_SIL_001",
      "category": "silence",
      "text": "......",
